headline.main: U.S. Energy Stocks, Darlings Last Year, Stumble in 2017
headline.print_headline: U.S. Energy Stocks, Darlings Last Year, Stumble in 2017

lead_paragraph: The energy sector is the stock market's dud so far in 2017 after a banner performance in 2016, and the rest of the year may also be rocky for investors due to the unclear path for crude oil prices.
